

=Bio=

'Ayan Mitra is CEO of CrowdBnk which he set up in 2011. He has over 13 years of extensive experience of delivering extremely complex systems in IT across the telecommunications, banking and retail industries to enable end to end business processes. Ayan completed MBA from London Business School in 2010. 

CrowdBnk is a crowdfunding platform that works with ideas across the entire spectrum - from charity, through social enterprise to for-profit businesses.  CrowdBnk is also the only FSA registered crowdfunding platform that offers retail investors the opportunity to directly invest in crowdfunded equity projects."


